snippet.title: Wayne's World gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Wayne's World, Dos PC game produced by Capstone in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/wayne-s-world/814/
Short presentation of Wayne's World, highlighting the chat system and story progression. A great game for all the fans of the real show.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Freddy Pharkas: Frontier Pharmacist - https://youtu.be/xoCLtT95BC4
